    <statement><p>Without any wind an airplane flies at <m>212\ {\textstyle\frac{\rm\mathstrut mi}{\rm\mathstrut hr}}</m>.  The plane travels <m>810\ {\rm mi}</m> into the wind and then returns with the wind in a total time of <m>7.67\ {\rm hr}</m>.  Find the average speed of the wind.</p>
<p>The wind's speed is <fillin characters="15" name="AnSwEr0001"/>.</p>
</statement>
    <answer>
      <p>
        <m>12.9208\ {\textstyle\frac{\rm\mathstrut mi}{\rm\mathstrut hr}}</m>
      </p>
    </answer>
